    "text": [
        "Dear Sir/ Madam,",
        "I am writing to express my interest in a part time job that you have advertised, in daily dawn newspaper on dated: 24th August 2022 on Sunday job classified section. I am keen interested in this post as part of my course.",
        "As, I am currently enrolling in Master Degree program and my major is in Finance, moreover, I want to exploit my skills and enhance my capabilities in that particular area of my interest. In addition, with, I have also done my SAP certification, which also brings efficiency and effectiveness in your system, beside this I have well versed knowledge about the accounting system along with good communication skills which are crucial for any restaurant. I am free from Monday to Tuesday between 2 to 6.",
